{"title":"Fasst Flexx Alloy weighs in heavier, more affordable suspension handlebar for MTB","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/11/more-affordable-vibration-damping-fasst-flexx-alloy-enduro-dh-bars-now-available/","date":1613052821000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>UK distributors Cyclorise have announced the addition of an alloy version of Fasst Company’s ground-breaking suspension handlebar, the Fasst Flexx Enduro and DH. The material update makes these eye-wateringly expensive MTB bars $100 cheaper than their carbon counterpart, now priced at $324.99.</p><p><em>Photos courtesy of Cyclorise</em></p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy.jpg\" alt=\"fasst flexx alloy suspension handlebar\" width=\"1200\" height=\"838\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-297x207.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-800x559.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-120x84.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-768x536.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-696x486.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-1068x746.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-601x420.jpg 601w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-100x70.jpg 100w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-297x207.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-800x559.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-120x84.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-768x536.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-696x486.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-1068x746.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-601x420.jpg 601w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/fasst-flexx-enduro-mtb-handlebar-alloy-100x70.jpg 100w\"></a></p><p>We got it, that is still a heap of cash to spend on a handlebar. Is it worth it? As always, it depends. We tested the original carbon Fasst Flexx Enduro bar and immediately saw tangible benefits to running a suspension handlebar. The vibration damping qualities in the load plane are second to none, while the bar remains super stiff in the steering axis.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><figure id=\"attachment_239696\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-239696\"><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/fasst-flexx-enduro-bar-dives-under-harsh-braking-medium-elastomers.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/fasst-flexx-enduro-bar-dives-under-harsh-braking-medium-elastomers.jpg\" alt=\"enduro mtb bar flex compliance reduced arm pump fasst co\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/fasst-flexx-enduro-bar-dives-under-harsh-braking-medium-elastomers.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/fasst-flexx-enduro-bar-dives-under-harsh-braking-medium-elastomers.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/fasst-flexx-enduro-bar-dives-under-harsh-braking-medium-elastomers-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/fasst-flexx-enduro-bar-dives-under-harsh-braking-medium-elastomers-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/fasst-flexx-enduro-bar-dives-under-harsh-braking-medium-elastomers-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-c